title: Kelsey Warren
text:
Hi! I’m Kelsey, a PhD student at the Institute of Arctic and Alpine Research (INSTAAR) at CU Boulder. I’m interested in all things mountains, forests, snow, and public health. Outside of academia, I love running, skiing, and cooking dinner with friends.

University of California, Santa Barbara (Bren) | Master of Environmental Science and Management | June 2025
University of California, Los Angeles | B.S. in Biology | June 2022



United Nations | Climate Adaptation Intern | June - September 2024
